data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch on a basement that is minutes to downtown Monroe. This is the perfect fixer that needs a little cosmetic work to make it your own. Roof, HVAC, and water heater are all under 5 years old.  This home features 3 bedroom, 2 full baths, a large living area and eat in kitchen. Kitchen includes refrigerator, microwave, stove, and dishwasher. The laundry room is located in the basement, washer and dryer included. Basement offers 2 partially finished rooms and access to the 2 car garage.  Large fenced in back yard is great for pets. Home sits on a .83 acre lot. This home is close to Highway 78, Highway 11, tons of shopping and eateries. Home is being sold AS-IS.
